ut it at the end. We call this 'escaping late.'<br><br>Besides protectin=
g yourself from a possible XSS vulnerability, escaping late makes sure t=
hat you're keeping the future you safe. While today your code may be onl=
y outputted hardcoded content, that may not be true in the future. By ta=
